.TP
.B /etc/dhcpdb.relay
Relay agent database
.TP
.B /tmp/addrpool_dump
Dump of the address pool database
.TP
.B /var/run/dhcps.pid
File which includes process ID (/var/tmp/dhcps.pid for NEWSOS)
.PD
